    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a dedicated project car or a source for parts. The engine currently has significant difficulty starting and will not maintain a steady idle, likely requiring a full overhaul. Structurally, there is extensive rust penetration along the rocker panels and wheel wells that will need professional metal work. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components, including the radio and power windows, are currently non-functional. It is being sold strictly 'as-is,' and we recommend towing it from the lot.",
      "price": 3800.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
